<select NAME="opSys" SIZE=1>
        <option value="unix">unix
        <option value="windows">windows
        <option value="macintosh">macintosh
</select>
<p>
Either paste in an RNA sequence or upload a FASTA format file containing
a single RNA sequence.
<p>
<b>Select the method of inputting the RNA sequence: </b>
<select NAME="inputType" SIZE=1>
        <option value="paste">type/paste one sequence
        <option value="upload">file upload of one RNA sequence
</select>
<br>

